And I think was Kamal Ghatak there as well?

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:53.500
Kamal Ghatak and there was some other people as well, isn't it?

00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:55.500
Kamal Ghatak and...

00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:57.500
Kamal Ghatak and...

